00:40:45.700 --> 00:40:50.520
of this briefly so that we get a sense of
what it's about. Take the Supreme Court. Normatively,

00:40:50.520 --> 00:40:55.200
the Supreme Court is supposed to function
like the American Supreme Court. But we bungle

00:40:55.200 --> 00:41:01.230
even in the initial stages, to be fair. Instead
of making it a constitutional code, which

00:41:01.230 --> 00:41:06.850
it ought to be in a very large, federal country,
we made also an appellate court and practically

00:41:06.850 --> 00:41:08.540
everything under the sun.

00:41:08.540 --> 00:41:13.931
And also we gave it original jurisdiction
on certain issues. The naturalities, in the

00:41:13.931 --> 00:41:18.780
United States, you know, Supreme Court, typically
