00:43:01.190 --> 00:43:04.350
So the notion what is federal, or what does
the federal government do, what does the state

00:43:04.350 --> 00:43:08.200
do, what does the local government do, what
does judicial do, what do the police do, what

00:43:08.200 --> 00:43:13.030
does bureaucracy do, what does legislature
do, what does executor do? There simply blurred

00:43:13.030 --> 00:43:18.090
lines, therefore, most people expect a legislator
to behave like an executor, and an executor

00:43:18.090 --> 00:43:23.570
to be actively important and vestful. Judiciary
actually wants to be all the time to be the

00:43:23.570 --> 00:43:24.620
executor, sometimes even the lawmaker.

00:43:24.620 --> 00:43:28.721
All kinds of things are happening. Distortions
are there. And when it come to the people,

00:43:28.721 --> 00:43:35.070
at the end of the day, in a system where the
word has no meaningful consequence in their

00:43:35.070 --> 00:43:40.370
lives, and this is a central fact, and in
a system where a few words more or less is

00:43:40.370 --> 00:43:45.410
gonna determine the political outcomes, in
an abjectly poor country what happened is

00:43:45.410 --> 00:43:50.510
a very natural thing. What's happening in
India in terms of money politics is a rational

00:43:50.510 --> 00:43:55.640
response to an irrational situation. It's
a perfect irrational response. I mean, if

00:43:55.640 --> 00:44:00.450
I were a citizen, if I know that nothing probably
of any consequence happen in terms of the

00:44:00.450 --> 00:44:03.930
outcome in the election, then I would try
to maximize my short term gain.

00:44:03.930 --> 00:44:04.930
&gt;&gt;audience1:
Right.

00:44:04.930 --> 00:44:06.450
&gt;&gt;JP:
And if a thousand rupees or two thousand pieces

00:44:06.450 --> 00:44:10.110
offered per vote, and this not an ab-, this
is not an abstract figure, it's a very real

00:44:10.110 --> 00:44:15.070
figure in India in several states, particularly
Andhra Pradesh, Tamil Nadu, Karnataka, etc.

00:44:15.070 --> 00:44:19.850
In an abjectly poor country there's big money.
And therefore, I try to maximize my short

00:44:19.850 --> 00:44:23.590
term gain. Others, the freebies after the
election, the free power and free color TV.

00:44:23.590 --> 00:44:29.200
Or emotional purchase because in a primordial
society, where caste and other loyalties are

00:44:29.200 --> 00:44:32.841
all important, and we haven't really enabled
people to discover that there's something

00:44:32.841 --> 00:44:36.480
more important than your caste, there's something
personal for your family. Better education

00:44:36.480 --> 00:44:40.051
for your children, maybe. Good health care
for your family, maybe. That's more important

00:44:40.051 --> 00:44:45.370
than your caste and religion. Unless we establish
that link, always this primordial loyalties

00:44:45.370 --> 00:44:46.420
be more important.

00:44:46.420 --> 00:44:51.770
And therefore, emotional purchase. And politicians
are perfect at the art of using these three

00:44:51.770 --> 00:44:56.570
purchases: directly buying the vote, offering
freebies for the vote, or giving emotional

00:44:56.570 --> 00:45:00.720
purchase in the form of caste, religion, and
language. And that's why we have to address

00:45:00.720 --> 00:45:06.590
in these three vests, local governments, citizen
central governments, electoral system, a fight

00:45:06.590 --> 00:45:11.120
against corruption. It can't be a one sector,
one [inaudible], there's no single silver

00:45:11.120 --> 00:45:13.920
bullet. I will say these are the five bullets
together.

00:45:13.920 --> 00:45:14.920
&gt;&gt;audience1:
Right.

00:45:14.920 --> 00:45:17.270
&gt;&gt;JP:
And unless we are understand adequately, I

00:45:17.270 --> 00:45:22.110
know all of the deeply concerned, but unless
the concern is informed by a deep awareness

00:45:22.110 --> 00:45:27.170
of what, what's the way forward, it could
be a really concern. We have to actually go

00:45:27.170 --> 00:45:28.980
forward. And that's my argument.

00:45:28.980 --> 00:45:30.250
&gt;&gt;audience1:
