00:46:32.820 --> 00:46:35.250
happen in the first place?

00:46:35.250 --> 00:46:40.490
When India became free, we had arguably, the
greatest galaxy of leaders ever assembled

00:46:40.490 --> 00:46:46.160
on the face of the earth. The only comparison
would be to the American Freedom Fighters

00:46:46.160 --> 00:46:50.310
and the Constitution makers, the Founding
Fathers of the United States. There is no

00:46:50.310 --> 00:46:56.950
other episode in history when such a galaxy
of liberal-minded, well-educated, deeply committed,

00:46:56.950 --> 00:47:02.680
great leaders came together with a common
purpose to build a nation. Post-independence

00:47:02.680 --> 00:47:07.880
was some time again, that caste played a role.
But subsequently, the best and the brightest

00:47:07.880 --> 00:47:15.190
society. They have given up on politics. They
have thought that they would pursue their

00:47:15.190 --> 00:47:19.430
own personal goals, which is of total their
right, that's what life is about, but at the

00:47:19.430 --> 00:47:25.230
cost of public domain. The vacuum is left
and the scum of humanity increasingly filled

00:47:25.230 --> 00:47:29.850
that. Or bad practices particularly took over.
In politics, too, like in economics, aggression's

00:47:29.850 --> 00:47:35.720
law operates. Bad politics always drives away
good politics. So, the answer really lies,

00:47:35.720 --> 00:47:40.750
in order to break this deadlock, this logjam,
in the middle classes, the educated people,

00:47:40.750 --> 00:47:45.751
the young people who are forward looking recognize
in the centrality of politics even to the

00:47:45.751 --> 00:47:50.050
economic future of the country. And playing
a role.

00:47:50.050 --> 00:47:54.620
Everyone doesn't have to simply give up everything
and then go and become a martyr or a farmer.

00:47:54.620 --> 00:47:59.910
Everybody can't go and become a contestant.
But we all have to play creative political

00:47:59.910 --> 00:48:08.220
roles as citizens from registration from voting
to voting sensibly and definitely to mobilizing

00:48:08.220 --> 00:48:12.510
other people to think rationally, to pursuing
rational policies, to enhancing the quality

00:48:12.510 --> 00:48:16.640
