practical about dealing with this matters.

00:50:22.460 --> 00:50:26.590
As I said before, our federalism has matured
remarkably. One of the great success stories

00:50:26.590 --> 00:50:31.270
of India is of federalism. In the past 25
years, there's been a steep change in federalism;

00:50:31.270 --> 00:50:36.802
we can be very, justly proud of that. It's
the only great example of a truly diverse

00:50:36.802 --> 00:50:39.160
society that models federalism after the United
States.

00:50:39.160 --> 00:50:43.180
