00:51:07.050 --> 00:51:11.540
stride. Except practical, political arrangements
and people are seeking. Now, how practical

00:51:11.540 --> 00:51:15.921
is it? Is it the best way forward, is something
that the nation must slowly debate and come

00:51:15.921 --> 00:51:20.580
to terms with it because the, the implications
are not going to be merely regional or limited

00:51:20.580 --> 00:51:25.740
to one state. They are going to apply to the
whole country. If language is not a marker,

00:51:25.740 --> 00:51:30.040
in a country where every non-Hindi state has
