00:51:30.040 --> 00:51:35.140
a new marker so that in, in Tamil Nadu, the
Northern part of the country, the Eastern

00:51:35.140 --> 00:51:39.020
or Western part of the country, demands now
crop up, how we deal with that will depend

00:51:39.020 --> 00:51:41.020
on what kind of markers we decide.

00:51:41.020 --> 00:51:45.690
There's nothing wrong in having markers. Like
an artisan in some parts, you can simply say,

00:51:45.690 --> 00:51:50.160
"I'll take this parallel and I'll take this
vertical, and that's it. I don't care how

00:51:50.160 --> 00:51:52.930
this state is created, but this is my state."
