00:51:52.930 --> 00:51:56.150
India wants. But you must also uniform principle.

00:51:56.150 --> 00:52:02.200
The second thing is the first part of India
where a region, which is host to the Capital

00:52:02.200 --> 00:52:06.340
City, unlike in United States, the capitalist
in India not only politically centralized,

00:52:06.340 --> 00:52:11.100
but also economically centralized, demographically
centralized. The hubs of economic growth,

00:52:11.100 --> 00:52:15.730
that region in all seem to have a separate
statehood. Until now, it's the far flung regions

00:52:15.730 --> 00:52:19.550
heavy from big cities that wanted a separate
