00:52:45.420 --> 00:52:49.760
it makes no difference. The real answer lies
in local governments, not in one state more

00:52:49.760 --> 00:52:53.150
or one state less. Neither integration nor
separation of a state is going to change anything

00:52:53.150 --> 00:52:57.330
monumentally. It's just going to create one
more Chief Minister in the Cabinet. Nothing

00:52:57.330 --> 00:52:58.330
more.

